Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:09.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:19.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:38.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:46.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:53.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:58.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:06.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.39,0:01:13.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.70,0:01:20.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.40,0:01:27.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:35.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I could've sworn it was\Nsomewhere around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:43.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:59.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Around this area, our nation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:03.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,...shares a border not only with\NShoukoku but also with the highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:09.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the spot where Shoukoku's\Naerial base was found the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:11.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was within the highland border.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:16.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,How would you interpret that in the\Nclearest and most pessimistic terms?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:21.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd have to say the highlands and\NShoukoku have formed an alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:23.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is the center doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:26.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:28.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,For the next few days, the Messis...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:32.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,...will dry-dock and undergo\Nmaintenance for our return trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:34.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know that times are grim...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:38.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but I hope you sibyllae\Nwill enjoy the time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:41.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's been far\Ntoo much tragedy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:47.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes... And most likely,\Nmore lies ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:53.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sacrosanct
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, someone was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:20.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Morinas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll leave right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:27.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. I'm going\Nto be a man myself after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still, that really blew me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:39.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who knew the Simoun gem\Ngauged people's emotions?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:44.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,It shows you that we understand\Nnothing about the Simouns even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:47.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,It does look that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:51.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said so yourself, remember?\NThat first day we met...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:57.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.\NI just remembered, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:00.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,S-Something\Ntells me this isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:04.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, you said this before.\NThat years ago, you and Floe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:08.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually, Floe and I used to be in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:10.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,I-In love?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:14.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, I didn't think\Nyou made a very good couple...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:22.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I tell you something now, will you\Nkeep it between the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:29.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's true I did harbor what could\Nbe called affection for Sibylla Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:31.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:35.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since she was\Na sacred sibylla, I just couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:38.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Take it to the next level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:40.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:44.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter how\Naggressively she pursued?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right. The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:49.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, Waporif.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,You and I were lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:55.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,If anyone asks, that's how\Nyou'll answer. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:06.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I won't tell anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:11.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,But a story this funny...\NI wonder if I can hold out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:13.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:21.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway... I don't know\Nabout the "sacred" part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:25.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we really be that big of a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:31.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,You feel that way because you have\Nyet to truly understand who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:36.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that's all there is to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that thing really gonna work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:42.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Be patient. Be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:44.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've seen it in a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:46.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:47.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here's one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:49.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina, that's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:53.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Para-sama, it's amazing!\NCome over here and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:57.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:01.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess Kaim's back\Nto calling her "Para-sama."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:13.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a lovely sound...\NThe laughter of young girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:16.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain, were we\Nreally like that once?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:21.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I have a feeling that\Nwe must have been once...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:23.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,But wait, were we really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,You called for me, Sibylla Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:40.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,First, let us pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:49.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I need something done in secret,\Nand I can ask no one but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns must\Nnever be violated...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:55.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,...as they are the holy\Nvessels of gods, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:56.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:59.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,And this divine vessel has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:01.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:06.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,You should already know\Nthe answer to that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:10.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you can't bring\Nyourself to say it, allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:15.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because the Simouns\Nare machines, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:18.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simoun gems,\Nwhich gauge our souls...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,The helical motors...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:23.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Granted, some mysteries remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:27.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, the truth\Nis just as you described.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:33.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns' undeniable superiority\Nover other nations has now been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:37.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the not-so-distant future,\Nthe military dynamic between...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:41.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Simulacrum Kyuukoku and our\Nneighboring countries will be reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:45.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dismantle a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:50.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're the one who said\Nthey were nothing but machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:54.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,With all due respect,\NSibylla Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:58.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that is something\Nwe've all been long aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:01.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,But people have looked\Nupon these "mere machines"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:05.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...as something divine and\Nsacrosanct, with love and respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:08.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,And why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:15.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because all we have are the Simouns.\NAll we have are the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:19.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,And to desecrate a Simoun\Nis something I simply cannot do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:28.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know it as well as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:38.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we can unlock all\Nof the Simouns' secrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:41.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,...our country,\NKyuukoku, will be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:47.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:51.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all this searching,\Nhow come we haven't found it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:52.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:57.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,They could've moved the base\Nbecause we found them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:01.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:04.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold on. If I'm right,\Nwe've got to check...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Turn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:18.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you're not even\Ngoing to ask my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:22.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just the two of us.\NWe can't bring it to a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:27.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't think we could ever\Nhave the same opinion, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:08.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd never before seen\Na cockpit mangled so badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,...until that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:17.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I could imagine the sheer shock\Nand pressure sustained in that blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:23.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,And then... when I had taken apart\Nthe twisted wreck of the cockpit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:26.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I didn't find Sibylla Amuria inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:30.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,But judging how\Nthe cockpit had been mangled...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:33.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it's not plausible that\Nshe'd been thrown out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:44.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,In that case,\Nwhere did Sibylla Amuria go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:49.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you made up your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:53.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought I had refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:58.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our neighboring countries are allying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:01.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,That aerial base is one good example.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:03.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Without us knowing a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:08.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Us"? Who do you\Nmean by "us," Sibylla Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:31.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did Dominüra want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:35.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, she said\NRimone's Simoun is malfunctioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:39.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:44.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a very good liar now, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:47.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:03.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:07.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,If Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:11.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rather, if anything happens,\NI want to take off at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:14.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,When the time comes,\NI want you to be my pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:20.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,The sum of one person's soul\Nis equal to everyone else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:27.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Should you overestimate its value,\Nthe decisions will be flawed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:31.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course, if our comrades\Nfind themselves in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:34.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it's a given that\NI would take off at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:44.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns are activated\Nby its two helical motors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:50.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, to be precise, you could\Nsay they're being manipulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:55.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,And beyond that fact,\Nwe know nothing about the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:58.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Waporif, don't tell me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said it once yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,That I should dismantle a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:20.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,After flying a Simoun...\Nsensing that Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:22.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I did learn something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:26.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,That they are divine vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:41.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,That they're sacred...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:47.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just like the sibyllae themselves,\Nthe Simouns are sacrosanct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:48.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:56.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I might be about to desecrate\Nthat which is sacred.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:12.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,They didn't get back tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:16.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just a reconnaissance mission.\NYou don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:17.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:22.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you think she's still\Nplanning to do an Emerald Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:27.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,They say things work out\Nif you're in love. If you love your pair...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:30.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it makes your\NRi Majons turn out right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:33.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on. That's what I told Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:38.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that right, Floe? Have you\Nreally ever experienced true love?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:40.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,True love?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:43.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't insult me!\NI'm always in true love...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:45.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you be quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:25.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you think\NI'm out of my element here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:28.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I promise it's a fine cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:32.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:36.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra,\Nyou must forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:40.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've looked into your background a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:45.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only remaining survivor\Nof the fabled Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Dextra...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:51.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Today, its very existence has\Nbeen erased from the records...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:56.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,...formed for the sole purpose of\Ncompleting the Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,A phantom chor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:04.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:07.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and the rest of\Nthe sibyllae lost their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:11.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,And now you're a sibylla under\Nthe military council's direct command.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:16.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,An appointment that even those\Nhigh priestesses had no say in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:25.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,You invited me to tea to discuss that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:33.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, to inform you that the plans\Nyou're about to execute...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:38.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,...are being watched\Nsilently by certain people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:45.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter what one intends,\Nin order to see it through...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:49.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we must all have something\Nto believe in wholeheartedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:51.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:54.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Something worth believing in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:56.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,That would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:58.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:13.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whether their\Nmystique is valid or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,...doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:12.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns\Nare machines, nothing more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:15.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,They are not\Ndivine vessels by any means.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:10.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,So it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:12.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:15.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I found nothing inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:20.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,At least, not anything\Nwe'd be able to comprehend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:26.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's there is nothing but a helix.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:30.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only thing we're\Ncapable of understanding is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:40.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:50.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:56.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:59.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're able to see\Nsomething, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can see something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:06.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:08.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:19.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,That voice just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:23.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:24.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go see what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:26.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go see what happened.\NShe's on the flight deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.04,0:21:30.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Take Sibylla Dominüra to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:30.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:32.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened? Is Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's all right!\NSibyllae, if you please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:39.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae, if you would\Nplease step aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:23.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? I just heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:26.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,...somebody crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:47.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:51.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.46,0:22:58.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:23:06.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:18.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:24.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.19,0:23:28.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.16,0:23:31.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:37.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.07,0:23:43.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:46.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:52.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:59.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.70,0:24:04.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.50,0:24:07.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shoukoku's upgraded aircraft...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.30,0:24:11.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,...are relentlessly threatening us,\Nand our forces are being scattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.84,0:24:14.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.81,0:24:15.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,One, and Then Another
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.08,0:24:17.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,One, and Then Another\NOne, and Then Another.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.38,0:24:19.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,One, and Then Another
